# RSI Percentile Calculator

This project downloads stock price data from Yahoo Finance and calculates RSI percentile thresholds.

It is built using Python and can be run locally or installed as a package.

---

## Installation

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/RSIpercentile.git
cd RSIpercentile
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Usage

Run the script:

```bash
python rsi_percentiles.py
```

You will be prompted to enter a stock ticker:

```
Enter stock ticker: AAPL
```

The program will print RSI percentile thresholds for the ticker.

---

## Requirements

- Python 3.9+
- yfinance
- pandas
- curl_cffi
- ta

